entries.speaker: ellie
entries.text: hi i am ellie thanks for coming in today i was created to talk to people in a safe and secure environment i am not a therapist but i am here to learn about people and would love to learn about you i will ask a few questions to get us started and please feel free to tell me anything your answers are totally confidential are you okay with this

entries.speaker: participant
entries.text: yes i am alright with this

entries.speaker: ellie
entries.text: okay so how are you doing today

entries.speaker: participant
entries.text: doing pretty good little bit tired

entries.speaker: ellie
entries.text: that is good where are you from originally

entries.text: i am from los angeles

entries.speaker: ellie
entries.text: really what are some things you really like about la

entries.text: the weather and the sports

entries.text: why

entries.text: i i get home late and i am usually up for like fifteen to like eighteen hours during the day so by the time i get home i am really not even that tired to go to sleep

entries.speaker: ellie
entries.text: that sucks
